data.title: The Dog Island (Video Game 2007)
data.meta_description: The Dog Island: In this single-player adventure, you play as a dog whose sibling falls very ill. Your only hope of saving her comes in the form of a special flower that only the keenest of "Sniff Masters" can find on The Dog Island.
